[
    {
        "content": "<p>I've found it confusing sometimes when working with Task and Result with the names of <code>onErr</code> verse <code>onFail</code>. I wonder if we could unify these to the same name? Should <code>Task.onFail</code> be renamed to <code>Task.onErr</code>?</p>\n<p>This is their current type signatures:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>Result.onErr : Result a err, (err -&gt; Result a otherErr) -&gt; Result a otherErr\nTask.onFail : Task ok a, (a -&gt; Task ok b) -&gt; Task ok b\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Note that both <code>Result ok err</code> and <code>Task ok err</code> are defined using <code>err</code></p>",
        "id": 368724849,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1687482018
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I've been wondering the same thing...if we did that, should we rename <code>Task.succeed</code> to <code>Task.ok</code>?</p>",
        "id": 368724896,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687482045
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>so both of them would have <code>ok</code> and <code>err</code></p>",
        "id": 368724911,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Feldman",
        "timestamp": 1687482056
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'll write an example to see how it looks</p>",
        "id": 368725009,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1687482101
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Elixir\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nc\">Command</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ls\"</span>\n<span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Command</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">arg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"-al\"</span>\n<span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Command</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">arg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dir</span>\n<span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Command</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">output</span>\n<span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Task</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">attempt</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">\\</span><span class=\"n\">output</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"ow\">when</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">output</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">status</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nc\">Ok</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">output</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">stdout</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Str</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">split</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"o\">|&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Task</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ok</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nc\">Err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nc\">ExitCode</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">code</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"n\">codeStr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Num</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">toStr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">code</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nc\">Task</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ls failed with exit code \\(codeStr)\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nc\">Err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">KilledBySignal</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nc\">Task</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ls was killed by signal\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nc\">Err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nc\">IOError</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nc\">Task</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">\"ls failed with IOError \\(err)\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 368725257,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1687482191
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>So we would have to also change <code>Task.fail</code> to <code>Task.err</code> too I assume</p>",
        "id": 368725288,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1687482211
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yeah I think so</p>",
